<xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" n="p.lond;1;22,r,p7" targOrder="U" to="DITTO" type="reprint from">PLond1,22pg7;PForshall3</xref></head><div lang="grc" part="N" type="edition"><ab part="N">
    <lb n="1"/>Σαραπίωνι ὑποδιοικητῆι 

    <lb n="2"/>παρὰ Τηγῆτος καὶ Ταῦτος 

    <lb n="3"/>διδυμῶν τῶν ἐν τῶι πρὸς 

    <lb n="4"/><choice><corr>Μέμφει</corr><sic>μεμφιν</sic></choice> μεγάλωι Σαραπιείωι. 

    <lb n="5"/>θεραπευουσῶν <add place="supralinear">ἡμῶν</add> ὑπὲρ τοῦ 

    <lb n="6"/>βασιλέως ἀξιοῦμεν, ἐάν σοι 

    <lb n="7"/>φαίνηται, ἐκθεῖναι ἡμῖν 

    <lb n="8"/>τὸ <choice><corr>γιν<supplied cert="high" reason="omitted">όμεν</supplied>ον</corr><sic>γινον</sic></choice> ἐλαίου μετρητὴν 

    <lb n="9"/>ἕνα τὸν ἐνιαυτόν, καθότι 

    <lb n="10"/>καὶ ταῖς προυπαρχούσαις 

    <lb n="11"/>ἡμῶν ἐν τῶι τόπωι ἄλλαις 

    <lb n="12"/>διδύμαις ἐγίνετο. ἐπεὶ καὶ 

    <lb n="13"/>τὸ <num value="6">ϛ</num> <expan><ex cert="high">ἔτος</ex></expan> εἰλήφαμεν ἕως 

    <lb n="14"/>Μεσορὴ <num value="30">λ</num>, ἀπὸ δὲ τοῦ 

    <lb n="15"/>Θῶυτ <expan><ex cert="high">ἔτους</ex></expan> <num value="7">ζ</num> οὐδὲν εἰλή-

    <lb n="16"/>φαμεν ποιούμεναι μεγά-

    <lb n="17"/>λας λειτουργίας τῶι θεῶι 

    <lb n="18"/>οὐδὲ τὰ γινόμενα ἡμῖν ἐ-

    <lb n="19"/>κ τ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ο</supplied>ῦ ἱεροῦ δέοντα, καθότι 

    <lb n="20"/>κα<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ὶ</supplied> ἔθος ἐστίν. ἐπεὶ οὖν 

    <lb n="21"/>τ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ὴν</supplied> καταφυγὴν ἐ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">π</supplied>ὶ σὲ πε-

    <lb n="22"/><choice><corr>ποι<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ή</supplied>μεθα</corr><sic>πεπο<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">η</supplied>μεθα</sic></choice>, μὴ περ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ιί</supplied>δῃς ἡ-

    <lb n="23"/>μᾶς ἀσθενῶς διακειμένας. 

    <lb n="24"/>τούτου δὲ γενομένου  ἔ-

    <lb n="25"/>σόμεθα τετευχυῖαι τῆς 

    <lb n="26"/>παρὰ σοῦ βοηθείας καὶ δι-

    <lb n="27"/>ὰ σὲ τὰς χρείας ἐπιτελοῦ-

    <lb n="28"/>σα<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ι</supplied> τῶι θεῶι. 

    <lb n="29"/>εὐτύχει. </ab></div><div n="meta.3408" part="N" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.3408" part="N" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date notBefore="-0163-03-08" type="textDate">nach  8. März 163 v.Chr.</date></p></div><div n="meta.3408" part="N" subtype="general" type="commentary"><p>Rückseite: UPZ I  86. </p></div><div n="meta.3408" part="N" subtype="mentionedDates" type="commentary"><head>Erwähnte Daten</head><p>Z. 13: <date notAfter="-0164" notBefore="-0165" type="mentioned">165 - 164 v.Chr.</date></p><p>Z. 14: <date type="mentioned" value="-0164-09-27">27. Sept. 164 v.Chr.</date></p></div><div n="meta.3408" part="N" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl><bibl subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">UPZ</title><biblScope type="volume">1</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">17</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">3408</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP"><series>0245</series>; <biblScope type="volume">1</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">17</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0245;1;17" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.3408" part="N" subtype="corrections" type="bibliography"><head>BL-Einträge nach BL-Konkordanz</head><bibl type="BL"><biblScope type="volume">IX</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">362</biblScope></bibl></div><div n="meta.3408" part="N" subtype="illustrations" type="bibliography"><p><bibl type="illustration">P.Lond. I, Facsimile I</bibl><bibl type="illustration">Pattie - Turner, Written Word, Plate 14, S. 37</bibl><bibl type="illustration">Pal. Soc. Mss., 2nd Ser., Bd. I, Pl. 22</bibl><bibl type="illustration">Seider, Paläographie III, 1, II Abb.82, S. 335</bibl></p></div><div n="meta.3408" part="N" subtype="otherPublications" type="bibliography"><head>Andere Publikation</head><bib